OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Sports Producer Joe
OL,8,FWardropper
OL,10,Finformed Mercedes the day before the
OL,11,Fshock news was announced to the world,
OL,12,Fteam principal Toto Wolff has revealed.
OL,14,FThe 52-year-old Austrian said he bore
OL,15,Fno grudge against the seven-time world
OL,16,Fchampion but admitted that "if you
OL,17,Ftold me two days ago that Lewis was
OL,18,Fgoing to Ferrari, I wouldn't have
OL,19,Fbelieved it."
