OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,FHamilton joined Mercedes in 2013, the
OL,8,Fsame year as Wolff, and the pair have
OL,9,Fenjoyed a close relationship, but the
OL,10,F39-year-old driver has not won a race
OL,11,Fsince losing out to Red Bull's Max
OL,12,FVerstappen in the final grand prix of
OL,13,Fthe 2021 world championship.
OL,15,FSpeaking for the first time since
OL,16,Fannouncing Hamilton's departure, Wolff
OL,17,Fsaid he broke the news to him in
OL,18,Fperson during a breakfast meeting at
OL,19,Fthe team boss' home in Oxford on
OL,20,FWednesday.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/8
