OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,F"We had a good hour of conversation...
OL,8,FHe said he has decided to race for
OL,9,FFerrari in 2025, and that was
OL,10,Fbasically it,' Wolff said.
OL,12,F"With me you can be very
OL,13,Fstraightforward, when he said this was
OL,14,Fthe fact, I didn't try and convince
OL,15,Fhim otherwise."
OL,17,FWolff maintained that his friendship
OL,18,Fwith Hamilton would survive the end of
OL,19,Ftheir racing partnership, and that he
OL,20,Fhad no reason to doubt his integrity.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/8
