OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,F"In the future we will discuss whether
OL,8,Fthis could have been handled in
OL,9,Fanother way, but I hold no grudge," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FAsked why Hamilton had left Mercedes
OL,13,Fmonths after signing a new contract,
OL,14,FWolff said: "I cannot tell you exactly
OL,15,Fwhat changed, I can only say we were
OL,16,Fvery aligned going into the Christmas
OL,17,Fperiod... You need to ask Lewis why he
OL,18,Fchanged his mind?"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
