OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,FBut Wolff said he understood
OL,8,FHamilton's decision to make a change,
OL,9,Facknowledging that, "every driver
OL,10,Fdreams of being in the red overalls,
OL,11,Fthe red car (of Ferrari)."
OL,13,FThe Mercedes boss also admitted that
OL,14,Fthe odds were against his team in the
OL,15,Fcompetition against Red Bull in
OL,16,FHamilton's final season with Mercedes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
