OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,FQuestioned about his hopes for
OL,8,FHamilton's future, Wolff said: "There
OL,9,Fis the friend side in me that says he
OL,10,Fshould have an eighth (title) because
OL,11,Fthat was taken away from him, so if he
OL,12,Fwins that in 2024 that would be a
OL,13,Fgreat thing, but going forward I would
OL,14,Frather us winning."
OL,16,FFerrari confirmed Hamilton's signing
OL,17,Fon a multiyear contract in a terse
OL,18,Fstatement released on Thursday.
