OL,3,C'I hold no grudge': Mercedes chief
OL,4,CToto Wolff on Hamilton's shock Ferrari
OL,5,Cexit
OL,7,FThe most storied and successful racing
OL,8,Fteam in motorsport history, Ferrari
OL,9,Fhas nevertheless failed to win a
OL,10,Fdriver's title since 2007, meaning
OL,11,FHamilton is not guaranteed
OL,12,Fchampionship success.
OL,14,FThe company's share price soared by
OL,15,Fmore than 10% on Thursday in response
OL,16,Fto the news.
OL,18,FHamilton will begin his final campaign
OL,19,Fwith Mercedes when the Formula 1
OL,20,Fseason begins in Bahrain in March.
